This is a PLACEHOLDER file, not a real SSH host key.

The actual host key is generated at build time by deploy/build-userspace.sh
and should NEVER be committed to git. Real keys are gitignored.

For QEMU testing, dropbear will generate a temporary key with the -R flag
(generate key on first connection) if no valid key file is provided.

For production nodes, provision unique host keys on first boot.
